  "description": "<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t●肯定结构:</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t1、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">Do型(即:动词原形(+宾语)+其它成分)。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:Please have a seat here. 请这边坐。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t有的祈使句在意思明确的情况下,动词可省略。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:This way, please. = Go this way, please. 请这边走。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t2、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">Be型(即:Be + 表语(名词或形容词)+其它成分)。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:Be a good boy! 要做一个好孩子!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t3、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">Let型(即:Let + 宾语 + 动词原形 + 其它成分)。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:Let me help you. 让我来帮你。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t●否定结构:</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t1、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">Do型和Be型的否定式都是在句首加don't构成。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:Don't forget me! 不要忘记我!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; Don't be late for school! 上学不要迟到!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t2、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">Let型的否定式有两种:&ldquo;Don't + let + 宾语 + 动词原形 + 其它成分&rdquo;和&ldquo;Let + 宾语 + not + 动词原形 + 其它成分&rdquo;。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:Don't let him go. / Let him not go. 别让他走。</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t3、<span style=\"color: #f00;\">有些可用no开头,用来表示禁止性的祈使句。</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t如:No smoking! 禁止吸烟!</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp; &nbsp; No fishing! 禁止钓鱼!</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p789966/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p789966\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p788805/\">英国脱欧明日公投 你需要科普的这里都有了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.